Usage: set_load [-help] <capacitance_value> <object_list> [-max] [-min]
                [-pin_load] [-subtract_pin_load] [-wire_load]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<capacitance_value>     # Capacitance value (float, required)
<object_list>           # List of objects: ports or nets (string, required)
-max                    # Specifies maximum capacitance (bool, optional)
-min                    # Specifies minimum capacitance (bool, optional)
-pin_load               # Specifies the external pin capacitance for a port
                        # (bool, optional)
-subtract_pin_load      # can be used only if nets are in object list
                        # (bool, optional)
-wire_load              # Interprets the specified capacitance as the external
                        # wire capacitance of the port (bool, optional)